2                               ! strat      - Speed control strategy
0.95							! dr_threshold 				- Threshold on absolute derating factor to trigger downregulation (keep normal operation for higher values)
180.0							! TfiltDerate_PWRCMD_HIST  	- Time constant for low-pass filtering of power setpoint for identification of downregulation phase [s] 
2								! smooth_dr_mode 			- smoothing method for demanded power (absolute derating factor) - 0: no smoothing, 1: rate limiter, 2: low-pass filter
0.05							! ddrmax 					- Maximum normalised power rate used in rate limiter, normalised by rated power [1/s] (used only when smooth_dr_mode=1) ! 0.025
30.0                            ! TfiltDerate_PWRCMD_SMOOTH  - Time constant for low-pass filtering of power setpoint for smoothing [s] (used only when smooth_dr_mode=2) 
60.0							! TfiltDerate_AVAILPWR 	    - Time constant for low-pass filtering of available power to limit derating factor[s] 
10.0 							! TorqueSatMargin			- Additional margin on miminum reference speed when derating to avoid torque saturation [%]
120.0							! TfiltDerate_SPD 			- Time constant for low-pass filtering of reference speed [s]
0.03    						! drrel_margin 				- Offset margin added to normalised available power to avoid overlimiting derating factor [-]
0                               ! limit_spd                 - Limit reference speed to measured speed in normal operation and restoration? 0: no, 1: normal operation only, 2: normal operation and restoration [-]
200.0                           ! KMinSat                   - Gain for torque PI control gain scheduling when derating close to minimum rotor speed
0.0                             ! ExclSpd                   - Excluded speed (center of speed exclusion zone) [rpm]
0.0                             ! ExclBand                  - Width of speed exclusion zone [rpm]
5.0                             ! Tkin                      - Time constant to convert available kinetic energy into power when limiting derating factor [s]. Tkin <=0 discards consideration for available kinetic energy.
-0.3                            ! PRC_SS_PCGain             - Custom setpoint smoother pitch control gain for use in derated operation
19								! MinCt_NDRs				- Number of derating factors (rows) in MinCt table
5								! MinCt_NCols				- Number of columns (quantities) in MinCt table, should be set to 5: Pitch, TSR, CT, CP, dCP (derating factor)
min_ct_table.IEA15MW.txt		! MinCt_filename			- File name of MinCt table
19								! MindCt_NDRs 				- Number of derating factors (rows) in MindCt table
20								! MindCt_NUs				- Number of wind speeds (columns) in MindCt table
min_dct_table.IEA15MW.txt		! MindCt_filename			- File name of MindCt table



